  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Substance Use Disorder has been showing a rising trend all over the world including India.
      The project tested whether a Integrated community wide effort of Prevention and Awareness
      Groups (PAG) to manage substance use would have a greater effect on treatment attendance and
      drug abstinence than a de-addiction program alone.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
